::Striker/Zenyak::

Zenyak rolls into a cave in the side of the island. Seeing Striker jerk up 
(Liono caught him), he uses the oportunity, grabs him, throws him against a 
wall of the cave, and shoots him in the chest.

Striker blinks in surprise, looking down at his smoking chest plate. He jumps 
at Zenyak, shoulder blasters shooting.
